data.description:
New lower price. *VA assumable loan 3.5%* This beautiful home is located in Edmond. Carpet was replaced 3 years ago. The home features a huge living area with a masonry fireplace. The large kitchen is a cooks dream. More counter space and storage than anyone will need. It has newer appliances and tastefully updated. It includes a nice breakfast space. The formal dining area will fit a large table. The half bath is conveniently located for guests. The bedrooms are large with great closets. The master bedroom will fit a king size bed with all of the accessories plus have room for a siting area. The master bath has been beautifully remodeled and updated as well as the guest bathroom. The large yard features lovely trees and landscaping, a great back patio and welcoming front porch. The neighborhood is family friendly and has beautiful older trees throughout. This home is close to I-35, Kilpatrick Turnpike, shopping and restaurants. 
*Reserve items Curtains, and Curtain rods.*
*VA assumable loan 3.5%*
